&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a very exciting opportunity for an experienced Administrator that would like to join us in the Social Services Department at the John Radcliffe Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post would be mainly to provide administrative support to the Adult Social Care and Community Services Team, also to maintain, train and develop Admin Staff working alongside the Admin Manager this includes our staff on both the Churchill and Horton sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main purpose of this post is to manage Admin staff within the social services Dept and assisting them in the reduction of delayed discharges for the Trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 9th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diana Ruffels. Social Services Administration Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: Diana.Ruffels@ouh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
